{"tid":1284703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登愛國網民：香港送5000億畀支那做無謂嘢","createTime":"2019-07-04T09:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T10:45:21.000Z","uid":205339,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bb3d7709165ebcf0e68eaa6bfda5ea53ff852298","tid":1284703,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:29:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家諗完左派，有冇諗過可以連右派都吸納埋？<br />\n大家有冇諗過從英國嘅民粹主義入手<br />\n依家英國脫歐搞到兩大黨固有力量動搖<br />\n依家為求自保會好受啲選民影響<br />\n我覺得可以利用<br />\n<br />\n英國精英主義離地同廢老保守民族主義大多數掌權<br />\n我覺得應該向住民族主義入手<br />\n依家brexit啲廢老俾人煽動晒覺得英國可以好似大英年代噉好威，對世界好有影響力，仲要大鑊到搞到兩大黨死噉滯<br />\n我地應該從依啲民粹心態入手<br />\n講香港係大英前國土，因為保守黨精英主義親歐親中背棄大英，自我貶低，放棄香港<br />\n依家全世界都反中國，大英前領土急要我地出手，英國仲要自貶做縮頭烏龜幾耐？save hong kong, our old friend. <br />\n仲要打經濟牌話香港送5000億畀支那做無謂嘢，英國可以駐軍保護嚟換錢拎嚟fund NHS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOur old friend Hong Kong be forced to send &pound;50Bn to China. Now they&rsquo;re seeking our help for democracy and freedom, be brave and stand up for Hong Kong!<br />\n之後再講&pound;50Bn可以fund NHS幾多幾多，英國海外軍費幾多幾多，dog whistle 引導佢地覺得嗰啲錢可以畀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">英國衛報已報警犬拉咗義士\nhttps://lih.kg/deoqGT\n#4 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n我覺得巴打講得好好<br />\n有無實際行動派支持<br />\n推俾大家見到<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">我無野講</code></pre>"},{"pid":"82156804a42e40d9e124c0e7e409174b1a1b3ea5","tid":1284703,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:32:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3d6a9c12a8ebf10c51b7555c5aaafb51f98830","tid":1284703,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:34:33.000Z","msg":"有無人有詳細行動計劃"},{"pid":"b96dc7b002f6110b2ab0d9b7d188b351aa6610fe","tid":1284703,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:35:45.000Z","msg":"<code>我無野講</code>"},{"pid":"84e8122b86a23b9e041e824669af5da5a9299c8d","tid":1284703,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228e41fc9e24f2a93d486b9cf4f9b50a01dc41ae","tid":1284703,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}